<sup>g</sup>Culture allows for antimicrobial susceptibility testing; culture sensitivity may be better when direct inoculation of specimen to selective media with carbon dioxide tablet at patient bedside; vancomycin in media may inhibit some GC strains.</p></fn><fn id="fn-212"><p>
